### ============================================================
### Mall Cloud — Order 模块接口测试脚本
### 直连订单服务端口（不经过 Gateway / BFF）
###
### 使用方式：IDEA 打开 → 点绿色箭头逐个运行
###
### Step 1：testLogin → 获取 Token
### Step 2+：后续请求自动携带 Token
### ============================================================

@ADMIN = http://localhost:8030
@ORDER = http://localhost:8026


### ============================================================
### Step 1：获取 Token（testLogin 跳过验证码）
### ============================================================

# @name testLogin
POST {{ADMIN}}/v1/auth/user/testLogin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}


### ============================================================
### Step 2：订单 C 端接口
### ============================================================

### 2.1 获取订单数量统计
# @name orderCount
GET {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/getUserOrderTradeCount
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### 2.2 分页查询订单
# @name searchOrder
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}

### 2.3 查询订单详情
# @name orderDetail
GET {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/detail/1
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

### 2.4 查询订单明细
# @name orderItem
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/getTradeItem
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"tradeCode":"TEST"}

### 2.5 订单确认/预览
# @name confirmOrder
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{}


### ============================================================
### Step 3：退货 C 端接口
### ============================================================

### 3.1 分页查询退货
# @name searchReturn
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/return/search
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}

### 3.2 退货详情
# @name returnDetail
GET {{ORDER}}/v1/mobile/trade/return/detail/TEST
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}


### ============================================================
### Step 4：B 端配送地址管理
### ============================================================

### 4.1 分页查询配送地址
# @name searchAddress
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/tradeDeliveryAddress/searchByPage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}

### 4.2 配送地址详情
# @name findAddress
GET {{ORDER}}/v1/tradeDeliveryAddress/findById?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}


### ============================================================
### Step 5：B 端退货审核
### ============================================================

### 5.1 分页查询退货申请
# @name searchReturnApproval
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/trade/return/searchByPage
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}

{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}


### ============================================================
### Step 6：统计接口
### ============================================================

### 6.1 订单统计
# @name orderStats
POST {{ORDER}}/v1/admin/trade/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{testLogin.response.body.data.token}}
